| **Week** | **Topics** 
|---|---|
| 1 | Introduction to Computers, Hardwares |
| 2 | Softwares, types of softwares |
| 3 | Number Conversions |
| 4 | Introduction to HTML |
| 5 | More about HTML and CSS |
| 6 | Introduction to DBMS |
| 7 | Queries in MySQL |
| 8 | Mid Term |
| 9 | Logic Building and Algorithm Designing |
| 10 | Introduction to Python, Basics of Python |
| 11 | Variables, basic operators, decision making in python |
| 12 | Loops, nested loops in python |
| 13 | Strings, arrays and lists in python |
| 14 | Introduction to AI |
| 15 | AI using Python |

