| **Week** | **Topics** |
|---|---|
| 1 | Allah (SWT) His signs- Comparison of information given in the Holy Quran about the creation of universe with that of modern science |
| 2 | Allah (SWT), His Oneness and His relationship with the human beings as explained in the Holy Quran. |
| 3 | Prophet (PBUH), His Place and Mission according to the holy Quran and his own blessed words. |
| 4 | Prophet (PBUH), His Seerah, Meccan period, Madinah period, Some lessons to learn from Messenger Madina and Farewell Pilgrimage. |
| 5 | The Holy Quran, General information, Preservation, Recitation and our Duties. Selected Verses from 2nd and 4th Chapter. |
| 6 | The Holy Quran, Selected Verses from 6th, 9th, 25th, 39th, 49th 61st Chapters. |
| 7 | Hadith, Basics of the Science of Hadith. Most used classifications. |
| 8 | Mid Term, Selected Ahadith.(20). |
| 9 | Islamic Faith- Belief in Angels, Books, Prophets and the Judgment Day. |
| 10 | Worships in Islam- Salah and Zakat |
| 11 | Worships in Islam- Fasting and Hajj |
| 12 | Islamic Civilization- Historical developments, its characteristics and influence over humanity |
| 13 | Basics of Islamic Jurisprudence |
| 14 | The Islamic Economic System |
| 15 | Human rights in Islam |

