| 2 | Analyzesimplealgorithmsanddeterminetheircomplexities | C | 4,5 |
| 3 | Apply the knowledge of data structures to other applications domain. | C | 3 |
| 4 | Implementbinarysearchtreeandperformtreebasedoperations. | C | 3 |

