| **Week** | **Topics** 
|---|---|
| 1 | Java Programming Environment, Primitive Data Types |
| 2 | Single and 2D Implementation Array |
| 3 | Single Link List, Double Link List , Link List Operations |
| 4 | Stack Implementation , Push , POP, Stack Implementation with Link List |
| 5 | Queue Operations |
| 6 | Linear Search, Binary Search, Recursion |
| 7 | Binary Trees, Insertion / Display in Binary Trees, Tree Traversal (Preorder, Post order, In order) AVL Trees : Insertion , Deletion , Search and Traversal |
| 8 | Mid Term |
| 9 | Heap Implementation and Operations ; Min Heap, Max Heap |
| 10 | Graph , Breadth First Search , Depth First Search |
| 11 | Minimum Spamming Tree, Dijkstra’s Algorithms |
| 12 | Hashing, Implementation of hash function, Hash tables, Insert, search and retrieve values from hash tables |
| 13 | Bubble Sort, Selection Sort and Its operations |
| 14 | Quick Sort, Merge Sort and Its operations |
| 15 | Insertion Sort Its operations and Complexity, Project |

