| 2 | Implement the relational database design and data modelingusingentityrelationship(ER)model. | C | 5 |
| 3 | Implement SQL: Data definition, constraints, schema, queries and operationsinSQL. | C | 2 |
| 4 | Produce well-structured database using functional dependencies and normalization,Build,designandtunedatabases. | C | 4 |

