## **CSCL 2203 Lab Database Systems**  

|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| **Programme:** | CS/SE/AI | **Degree:** | BS | **Semester:** | 4 | **Credits:** |  |
| **Course Code:** | CSCL 2203 | **Course:** | Lab Database Systems | **Course Type:** | Core | | |
