| 3 | Analysis of Processor and Memory Performance: Assess the ability of students to analyze processor behavior and memory performance using metrics such as CPI (Cycles per Instruction), pipeline efficiency, cache hit/miss rates, and memory access times. Assessment can be through problem-solving exercises, performance calculations,orcasestudies. |
