| **CLO** | **Description** | **Domain** | **BT Level** |
|---|---|---|---|
| 1 | Apply matrices, determinants, and linear systems to computing problems | C | 3 |
| 2 | Analyzevectorspaces,spanningsets,bases,anddependence | C | 4 |
| 3 | Evaluate inner products, eigenvalues, diagonalization, and transformationsforCSmodels | C | 5 |

