| 2 | Analyze and evaluate the algorithms of the core functions of the operatingsystemsandexplainthemajorperformanceissueswith regardtothecorefunctions | C | 4,5 |
| 3 | Demonstrate the knowledge in applying system software and toolsavailableinmodernoperatingsystem. | C | 3 |

