## **CSCL 3107 Lab Operating Systems**  

|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| **Programme:** | CS/SE/AI | **Degree:** | BS | **Semester:** | 5 | **Credits:** |  |
| **Course Code:** | CSCL 3107 | **Course:** | Lab Operating Systems | **Course Type:** | Core | | |
