| Develop an understanding of community service, social responsibility, and ethical engagement. Apply technical and problem-solving skills to contribute to community-based initiatives. Enhance teamwork, leadership, and communication through hands-on social projects. Foster awareness of societal challenges and strategies for impactful change. Encourage lifelong  |
**Course Description**  
civic engagement and volunteerism. || |  
|-|  
| This course provides students with experiential learning opportunities through community engagement, volunteerism, and social impact projects. Students will collaborate with NGOs, community organizations, and social enterprises to address real-world challenges, applying their technical skills and AI knowledge to support community development. The course fosters civic responsibility, teamwork, and ethical decision- making. | |
