| 2 | Analyze organizational structures, employee relations, HR practices, and software contracts in the context of professional ethics. | C | 4 |
| 3 | Apply professional codes of conduct (ACM, IEEE, BCS) and ethical frameworks toreal-worldscenarios. | C | 3 |
| 4 | Evaluate legal responsibilities, accountability, auditing, and social implications ofcomputingpractices. | C | 5 |

