## **CSC 4105 Final Year Project-I**  

|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| **Programme:** | Computer Science | **Degree:** | BS | **Semester:** | 7 | **Credits:** | 3 |
| **Course Code:** | CSC 4105 | **Course:** | Final Year Project-I | **Course Type:** | Core | | |
